summary: A small player home Suited to a hunter has 8 mannequins, 20 Weapon racks and display cases as well as teleporters and vault room
descriptionHtml:
A small player home north of Falkreath hidden away in a secluded forest for the dragonborn to relax in. Includes 8 mannequins, 20 Weapon racks, Personal fishing area, Archery range, Treasue room, Teleports from cabin to 7 main factions and more!

On a small note please do not upload this file to any other websites without my permission so i can keep track of this mod and keep it up to date.

If you have any problems or improvements let me know :)
Hope you like it and enjoy!


Screenshots taken with:
Sharpshooter's ENB Classic: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15105/?
I also Highly Recommend Enhanced Lights and FX: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/? (without the lighting will be darker and faded)

THANK YOU to everyone who has supported this mod and put so many great ideas foward.

Also on Steam workshop: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=161364896
